subproject.corporate outcome: Improved capacities of AU and RECs to elaborate regional frameworks for economic governance and to monitor and evaluate the performance of service delivery
subproject.description: By deepening existing partnerships and developing new ones, it is intended to provide coherent and coordinated support to the various priority areas of NEPAD and APRM resulting with joint missions, joint programming and joint reporting. It also aims at rationalizing and strengthening existing mechanisms for consensus building, promote mutual learning and experience of best practices.
subproject.gender code: No noticeable contribution to gender equality
